channel.title: How to change levels u needd to smith items
channel.description:
well i made this to my server that u can smith rares.
but ive got a problem with it,
it always say the level is too low .
so how to change levels u need for smithing items?
thank you :D

item.title: How to change levels u needd to smith items
item.dc:creator: @kupo kupo
item.description:
@kupo wrote:

Search for the level that it is or just search down an item ID from the smithing list, then eventually you’ll see a list of the stuff you can smith and you can change the levels on there. Or if you need to change the level under it you have to edit sendframe…like sendframe126(TEXT, ID);
